             <lg> 
              <l>The butterfly is a thing behold,</l>
          <l>with colors more beautiful than gold.</l> 
          <l>Flying hour by hour,</l>
          <l>going from flower to flower.</l>
          <l>Oh, how I enjoy your beauty butterfly,</l>
          <l>as I sit and watch you flutter by.</l>
          
                 
